  "text": "Under the Assumptions 1-5 it is a well known result that the solution and multipliers are unique [CITATION_1] . We make the following assumption on the iterate v k based on the indices of y * i that are not at the bound, i.e. i > n a . This is the requirement of correct identification of inactive constraints that we described in Section 1.1.",
